text: Alonso Mariscal Abascal (25 January 1914 - 31 January 1959) was a Mexican diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1932 Summer Olympics. He is the brother of Olympic divers Antonio Mariscal, Federico Mariscal, and Diego Mariscal. ==Notes== ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1914 births Category:1959 deaths Category:Mexican male divers Category:Olympic divers of Mexico Category:Divers at the 1932 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City
